author: Andrew Roberts
title: Alec Baldwin Can't Cope With Stress of Impending 'Rust' Trial: Report
text:
Alec Baldwin may be sweating heavily more and more ahead of his upcoming Rust manslaughter trial . On the heels of Hannah Gutierrez-Reed's guilty conviction for involuntary manslaughter and her maximum sentence of 18 months, Baldwin is now preparing for his trial in July and fighting at each turn .
According to The Blast , both deal with the accidental shooting on the set of Rust that injured director Joel Souza and killed cinematographer Halyna Hutchins. Gutierrez-Reed was the armorer on the set and was responsible for the firearm that was fired in Baldwin's possession.
Baldwin's charges were initially dropped in April 2023 but a later FBI report concluding the gun couldn't have gone off without the trigger being pulled reopened the case in January. Baldwin has already pleaded not guilty and is reportedly ready for the situation to be finished.
"It continues to be a very stressful situation for Alec and Hilaria. A not guilty verdict for Hannah would have caused less stress," a source reported told PEOPLE . "He still trusts his defense though. They just want the trial over with."
According to Fox News, the prosecution team has added another member to join special prosecutors Kari Morrissey and Jason Lewis, appointing Erlinda Johnson for the role. "Whoever handles the firearm has a duty to check it for any live rounds," Johnson said to PEOPLE back in 2021 . "[There's] a lot of civil liability here. It's going to be a nightmare..."
Some good news for Baldwin is the family of Halyna Hutchins has dropped their latest lawsuit against the actor . The suit was dropped without prejudice and could be filed again at a later date.

title: Alia Bhatt Gets 'Goosebumps All Over' After Watching Vicky Kaushal's Chhaava Trailer
text:
Alia Bhatt Gets ‘Goosebumps All Over’ After Watching Vicky Kaushal's Chhaava Trailer
Alia Bhatt lauds Vicky Kaushal's Chhaava trailer, calling it 'breathtaking' and admitting it gave her 'goosebumps all over.'
Vicky Kaushal’s much-awaited historical drama Chhaava has been generating buzz ever since its trailer dropped on January 22, 2025. Featuring Rashmika Mandanna and Akshaye Khanna alongside Vicky, the power-packed trailer has received praise from fans and celebrities alike. After Katrina Kaif, Alia Bhatt also shared her thoughts, calling the trailer “breathtaking" and admitting it gave her “goosebumps all over."
Taking to her Instagram stories, Alia shared the trailer and expressed her admiration, writing, “The trailer is absolutely breathtaking. Goosebumps all over. All the best (red heart emoji)," while tagging Vicky Kaushal and Rashmika Mandanna.
related stories
Earlier, Katrina Kaif, Vicky’s wife, had also praised the trailer on her social media, expressing excitement with, “Outstanding #DineshVijan. This is just (multiple fire emojis)," tagging filmmaker Laxman Utekar, Vicky, Rashmika, and Akshaye.
For those unfamiliar, Chhaava is a historical action film that features Vicky Kaushal in the role of Chhatrapati Sambhaji Maharaj, while Rashmika Mandanna portrays Maharani Yesubai. Akshaye Khanna takes on the role of Mughal emperor Aurangzeb. The film boasts a stellar ensemble cast, including Ashutosh Rana, Divya Dutta, Vineet Kumar Singh, Diana Penty, and Santosh Juvekar, all in significant roles.
The film, helmed by Laxman Utekar and produced by Dinesh Vijan, promises to bring to life the valor and sacrifice of the Maratha warrior. The grand visuals, intense action sequences, and powerful performances glimpsed in the trailer have left audiences eagerly awaiting the film’s release.
Fans have flooded social media with positive reactions, lauding the film’s production value, Vicky’s commanding presence, and Rashmika’s regal portrayal. Many believe Chhaava will be another milestone in Vicky Kaushal’s career, further cementing his reputation as one of Bollywood’s most versatile actors.
With endorsements from industry stalwarts like Alia Bhatt and Katrina Kaif, the anticipation surrounding Chhaava continues to soar, setting the stage for an epic cinematic experience.

title: Papa Francesco: incontro per l’80° delle Acli. “Vostra storia patrimonio da cui trarre energie vitali per guardare avanti con speranza” - AgenSIR
text: Papa Francesco ha ricevuto oggi in udienza, nell’aula Paolo VI, le Acli (Associazioni cristiane lavoratori italiani) in occasione dell’ottantesimo anniversario dalla loro fondazione. “Sono felice di accogliervi mentre state celebrando il vostro ottantesimo anniversario. È una storia lunga e ricca, che testimonia il vostro impegno e la vostra dedizione nel servizio alla comunità”, ha esordito Bergoglio nel suo intervento. “Avendo ottant’anni siete un po’ più giovani di me, ma il vostro percorso è molto significativo; e questo anniversario è una buona occasione per rileggere la vostra storia, con le sue gioie e i momenti difficili, e per esprimere gratitudine. Ringrazio con voi il Signore che vi ha accompagnato e sostenuto lungo questo cammino, anche ispirando tante persone che, attraverso le Acli, hanno dedicato la loro vita al servizio dei lavoratori, dei pensionati, dei giovani, degli stranieri e di tanti che si trovano in situazioni di bisogno”. Le Acli, ha aggiunto il Papa, sono un luogo dove è possibile incontrare dei “santi della porta accanto”, che “non finiscono sulle prime pagine dei giornali, ma a volte cambiano concretamente le cose, in bene”. “Questa storia è un patrimonio da cui trarre energie vitali per guardare avanti con speranza e determinazione. In essa troviamo i valori che hanno ispirato i vostri fondatori e che generazioni di aclisti hanno incarnato nel corso degli anni, attraverso una presenza importante nella società”.

發佈時間：18:45 2024-08-30 字體大小 以往香港被譽為美食天堂，各國飲食應有盡有，但近年來不少餐廳的食物質素卻備受批評，就連連鎖餐廳也不例外。近日，有港人在社交平台上發文，指自己用外送平台叫外賣Pizza，用$29加購了3件烤雞，但是送上來的食物卻與想像中的「烤雞」有很大差距，讓事主直言：「收到真係呆左」。
叫外賣Pizza加購3件烤雞 卻收到如「手指咁大」雞塊 近日，有港人在Facebook群組 「飲食黑店大全（全港食店質素/價錢/服務關注組）」 上發文，指自己在外送平台上，叫了某連鎖餐廳的外賣Pizza，用$29加購了3件烤雞。但是送來的這3件「烤雞」，卻每件都只有「手指咁大」，讓事主直言：「收到真係呆咗」，並希望該餐廳可以解釋一下，「可能我無知啦，唔知其他谷友有冇叫過？1件件嘅烤雞真係咁？」， 即點擊上文圖輯查看詳情！
網友留言：以後唔幫襯 帖子引來網友熱議，有網友對於「烤雞」的分量感到驚訝，「三件、三塊、三條係唔同嘅野，相入面只能叫3條雞肉」、「的的確確係『3件』」、「佢嘅烤雞真係3塊雞片嚟，厚少少嘅雞片」。亦有網友認為餐廳太過分，「我以為係肥豬肉...」、「我以為係殘肢嚟」、「有雞的DNA就冇犯法，唯有之後不幫襯」、「擺明係雞飯啲淨料」、「以後唔幫襯」、「而家大多數北上深圳或者澳門消費」。
